Subject: [PATCH 5.4 058/270] drm/nouveau/kms/nv50-: Fix disabling dithering
Date:   Mon, 17 Aug 2020 17:14:19 +0200
Message-Id: <20200817143758.665239242@linuxfoundation.org>
